{"tid":637078,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"連登幾時開公審台？","createTime":"2018-04-21T13:12:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-28T19:59:36.000Z","uid":3189,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3cfbc45c7a5e7429f3e54c6bc43887155d4912e7","tid":637078,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T13:12:12.000Z","msg":"比人呃錢，公審。<br />\n<br />\n發現厹，公審。<br />\n<br />\n知道某人係ptgf，公審。<br />\n<br />\n我認為連登應該有一個新分台 - 公審台<br />\n<br />\n將公審post集中係一個分台下<br />\n<br />\n除左可以令其他會員能夠清楚睇到近期被公審既人<br />\n<br />\n而開帖者無需要係不確定既分台開公審Post<br />\n<br />\n例如：吹水台，創意台，感情台等等<br />\n<br />\n從而令閱讀者集中一個分台<br />\n<br />\n增加公審既效應<br />\n<br />\n眼見每日都有兩，三個公審Post活躍<br />\n<br />\n甚至上埋熱門<br />\n<br />\n公審Post已成連登新趨勢<br />\n<br />\n所以開公審台係相當有急切性去應付呢股潮流"},{"pid":"d6dc2c6d2a624bd33192ba16c240be2149b19a4e","tid":637078,"uid":129039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T13:13:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"333df0658325f91238ad19143f077c307f458a8b","tid":637078,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T08:16:40.000Z","msg":"lauming"},{"pid":"ce2ef708bcf7d3d625f546f94d0f95906640effa","tid":637078,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T08:21:38.000Z","msg":"lau ming"},{"pid":"96c7025d2afdcf2ca9885cf1973cee36745ff829","tid":637078,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T13:54:09.000Z","msg":"係囉"},{"pid":"e6ab4c0e4d3398bb70215989be8659aa715a8071","tid":637078,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T15:17:14.000Z","msg":"幾時"},{"pid":"aa3ef0f3f896e91d31dcc4c32e92607c6721e07b","tid":637078,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T19:57:58.000Z","msg":"lau ming"},{"pid":"e3455f0edbff5a9f97478ddb8ee9c999369d7f32","tid":637078,"uid":45148,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-0